@node Ai2 "Aural illusion v2.0"

You've made your new sounds but now what...

Edit, Create and Mutate your samples in :

Aural illusion v2.0


Now with 30 Variable Effects including:
---------------------------------------
Time Stretch, 
Graphic Equalizer, 
Mixer, 
Resonant Filter, 
Compress, 
Gate, 
Reverb, 
Echo, 
Chorus, 
Flange, 
Phase Shift, 
Stereo Processor,
and more...


55 Manipulations including:
---------------------------
8 Tunings, 
6 Modulations, 
8 Filters, 
12 Arithmetic/Logic functions,
9 Waveshaping functions,
and others as well.


16 Bit "Morphing Wave" synthesizer with:
----------------------------------------
8 mixable wave types, 
4 step Wave Morphing,
Sample wave grabbing, 
Envelope Generator,
Phase controls for improved sound.


Editing Functions including:
----------------------------
Loudness, 
Get Frequency, 
Swap, ReScale, 
Recreate, 
Cut,
Copy Over, 
Copy into, 
Zero,
and many more.


Supports various 8 and 16 bit file formats:
-------------------------------------------
IFF, 
AIFF, 
AVR, 
WAV, 
VOC, 
MAUD,
SAFF, 
RAW 8,
RAW 8 PC,
RAW 16,
RAW 16 LSB, 


All processing done in 32 bit format,
samples held in 16 bit format.

Requires Workbench v2.04 or greater and 2 Meg RAM.

